25
00:02:14.110 --> 00:02:18.550
The next layer is Layer 3, the Network Layer.

26
00:02:18.730 --> 00:02:25.510
The most important information at the Network Layer is the source and destination IP address.

27
00:02:25.510 --> 00:02:33.130
